SoftwareProduct.application: Microsoft Internet Information Services (IIS) Manager for Remote Administration
SoftwareProduct.description: Microsoft Internet Information Services (IIS) Manager for Remote Administration allows remote management of web servers running IIS. It provides a graphical user interface for managing websites, virtual directories, applications, and other IIS settings. It enables administrators to remotely control and monitor web servers, making it convenient for managing multiple servers from a single location.
